import { FiSearch } from 'react-icons/fi';


import {
    LogoImage,
    HeaderSectionContainer,
    HeaderSection,
    HeaderTitle,
    HeaderInputContainer,
    HeaderInput,
    HeaderSearchButton,
    AnotherRoute

} from './styles';

const Input = () => (
    <HeaderSectionContainer>
    <LogoImage placeholder={"Digite o usuário..."} src={'https://image.flaticon.com/icons/png/512/25/25657.png'} alt={"Logo do GitHub"} />
    <HeaderSection>
        <HeaderTitle>Digite o nome do usuário:</HeaderTitle>
        <HeaderInputContainer>
            <HeaderInput />
            <AnotherRoute href={"/Home"}>
            <HeaderSearchButton>
                <FiSearch size={15} />
            </HeaderSearchButton>
            </AnotherRoute>
        </HeaderInputContainer>
    </HeaderSection>
    </HeaderSectionContainer>
);

export default Input;
